---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "@/components/Section.astro";
---

<Layout title="Fajar Maftuh Fadli">
  <Section>
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-black text-slate-50">Fajar Maftuh Fadli</h1>
    <div class="mb-8">
      <p>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          Hey! I'm Fajar Maftuh Fadli <img
            src="/icons/waving-hand.svg"
            alt="Waving Hand icon"
            class="h-5 w-5 animate-bounce cursor-grab invert"
          /></span
        > a DevOps engineer who cares about clean, reliable infrastructure.
      </p>
      <ul class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <li><a href="/projects">View Projects</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cv">View CV</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#contact">Contact Me</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p>
      I'm currently working at <a
        href="https://www.fisclouds.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">FISClouds</a
      >, where I design and manage cloud systems—mostly on Google Cloud
      Platform. I work a lot with Terraform to automate infrastructure, handle
      IAM at scale, and setting up monitoring and alerting so things stay
      reliable and predictable in production.
    </p>
    <p>
      Most of my experience comes from real production environments, so I care a
      lot about reliability, cost efficiency, and making systems easy to observe
      and maintain.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of that, I've been getting into frontend and web development,
      mainly in the JavaScript ecosystem. It's fun designing things—lining
      everything up, making them interactive, and building something that
      actually looks good, not just infrastructure hidden somewhere in the
      cloud.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not working, I'm usually gaming, watching movies or series, or
      ricing my <a href="https://github.com/froggologies/dotfiles">setup</a>.
    </p>
    <div id="contact" class="my-16">
      <p>You can find me here:</p>
      <ul class="flex gap-4">
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/froggologies"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <img
              src="/icons/github.svg"
              alt="GitHub icon"
              class="h-5 w-5 invert"
            />
            GitHub
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/fajarmaftuhfadli"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <img
              src="/icons/linkedin.svg"
              alt="LinkedIn icon"
              class="h-5 w-5 invert"
            />
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://steamcommunity.com/id/froggologies"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <img
              src="/icons/steam.svg"
              alt="Steam icon"
              class="h-3 w-5 invert"
            />
            Steam
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="flex items-center gap-2">
        Or mail me at <a
          href="mailto:fajarmaftuhfadli@gmail.com"
          class="flex items-center gap-2"
          ><img
            src="/icons/gmail.svg"
            alt="Gmail icon"
            class="h-5 w-5 invert"
          />fajarmaftuhfadli@gmail.com</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
